---
title: Miso-Glazed Eggplant & Sesame Greens with Creamy Coconut Rice
description: Introducing the newest member of the HelloFresh family: miso paste! You may know it from the classic Japanese soup but this superstar ingredient adds a deep, umami rich flavour to anything it touches - one taste and we know you’ll be hooked. Here, you’ll make a sweet and salty miso glaze that transforms eggplant into a caramelised and roasted delight. With creamy coconut rice and flavoursome greens, this is a vegetarian feast on a plate.
